title: The Wild Beyond the Witchlight
content:
The Wild Beyond the Witchlight begins on the outskirts of a city, then ventures into the Feywild, a place of wonder and whimsy ruled by unfettered emotion. The players have memories as children when they visited the wonderous Witchlight Carnival, they remember rides, attractions, and food. However, they all have a distinct feeling of not returning home whole. Itâ€™s now been many years, and the players find themselves once again at the front of the fey carnival.
